  "description": "<p><strong>Customer Service Officer</strong></p><p>Basic Salary: $2000 - $2200<br />Working hours:  Mon - Fri: 8am-5pm, Alt Sat: 8am to 12pm<br />Working Location: Pandan Loop (Clementi)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with placement of orders via phone, email, mail or fax</li><li>Keep records of customer interactions, process customer accounts, and file documents</li><li>Open and maintain customer accounts by recording account information</li><li>Versed with AutoCount software, for invoicing and back-of-house logistics management between Sales and Warehousing teams</li><li>Ability to multi-task and prioritize workload and adapt to changing procedures and processes.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties assigned as and when required by superior</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Secondary School/ O Level or any equivalent</li><li>Min 1 year of relevant working experience</li></ul><p><br />Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
